column5: Had to cancel my sister & my trip Aug 20-27 at Uchi Lake due to Sister's husband needing a heart operation. The deposit's were forwarded to next year so we will go next year!!
Sorry to hear that, hope everything goes ok for him!
That's awfully Larry.Hope everything turns out for the better.

Thanks John & 7 Mag . Deposit is good for next year ,we will be coming to Uchi next year. Heading to Wisconsin Sept 9 for a week to my wives relatives .Will also stay at my cousin's who lives in Sturgeon Bay and will be going fishing for a couple of times. Good Fishing to Everyone Larry S
